name: Urgent Crisis Situation
description: Story with high urgency markers and safety concerns
transcript: This is an emergency. My name is Maria Rodriguez. I'm in immediate danger. I fled my home yesterday because of domestic violence. I'm currently hiding in a friend's house with my three children. We have nothing - no clothes, no food, no money. I desperately need emergency shelter, food, and protection. I'm in Phoenix, Arizona. Please, I need help urgently. My safety and my children's safety are at risk. I can't go back home. I need emergency assistance right now. You can reach me at maria.emergency@gmail.com. This is a crisis situation.
